    "For Twitter, user statistics are as follows: 18-29 (13% usage), 30-39 (8%), 40-49 (7%), 50+ (1%) 48.",
    "We provide an overview and descriptive statistics on all user attributes as available from the API in Supplementary Table 4.",
    "The relevant user attributes for our main results and their assigned names are described in the following.",
    "Followers are the number of accounts that follow a user.",
    "Followings reports the number of accounts a user is following."
